This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, To assess the effect (harms and benefits) of nitrates in comparison with placebo or other drugs for treating chronic heart failure. To assess the effect of a combination of nitrates with other drugs in comparison with placebo or another pharmacotherapy; to assess the effect of different nitrates compared with each other (nitroglycerin, isosorbide dinitrate and isosorbide mononitrate). To assess the effect of different administration formulation of the same type of nitrates